pr_body: Following my GSoC project this year as described here ( https://dokuwiki.librecad.org/doku.php/gsoc:gsoc2022 ) I'm pushing this changes that should create a new action in Github Actions that can be launched manually by the developers. It will build the current version of LibreCAD and upload the binaries for Windows in form of an EXE, and for Linux in form of an AppImage and a Snap. The exe should be portable though I have not tested if it is.
